FBIS4-3982 "drchi082_a_94010" FBIS-CHI-94-082 Daily Report 28 Apr 1994 INTERNATIONAL AFFAIRS General Foreign Ministry Holds Weekly News Briefing Foreign Ministry Holds Weekly News Briefing Malaysian Prime Minister To Visit OW2804081994 Beijing XINHUA in English 0811 GMT 28 Apr 94 OW2804081994 Beijing XINHUA English BFN [Text] Beijing, April 28 (XINHUA) -- At the invitation of Chinese Premier Li Peng, Prime Minister Mahathir Mohamed of Malaysia will pay a working visit to China from May 11 to 13. This was announced by a Chinese Foreign Ministry spokesman here this afternoon. During his visit, the Malaysian prime minister will attend a high-level international economic forum, according to the spokesman.
